JO  - AMR
SP  - 445
EP  - 458
VL  - 14
IS  - 3
PB  - Academy of Management
N2  - Research on the grievance system has focused on one of two questions: why do employees file grievances or what is the impact that the grievance system has on employee behavior? This article presents a conceptual framework that integrates perspectives of both questions. Attention also is given to the degree to which research supports the framework's components. Implications for theory and research are suggested.
AB  - Research on the grievance system has focused on one of two questions: why do employees file grievances or what is the impact that the grievance system has on employee behavior? This article presents a conceptual framework that integrates perspectives of both questions. Attention also is given to the degree to which research supports the framework's components. Implications for theory and research are suggested.
